{"tid":2155990,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"阿里巴巴新公司叫京西 因為在北京西邊","createTime":"2020-08-14T07:00:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T12:25:04.000Z","uid":339805,"like":162,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"1023748f0acbdd321ed52adce65d8f117aba93c3","tid":2155990,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:00:45.000Z","msg":"阿里巴巴(9988)、京東(9618)近年來港上市得到更多人認識，而近日阿里巴巴註冊的一間新公司，名為阿里巴巴京西信息科技，而京西業務亦包括產品銷售，正好與京東一樣。<br />\n<br />\n阿里雲官方微博指，新公司「搞高科技數據中心和新基建的。因為註冊地在北京西邊的張家口，所以叫『京西』」。<br />\n<br />\n內地網民對此作出各種評論留言，包括呼籲註冊「阿外巴巴」反擊、京東應註冊「阿西巴巴」；而騰訊(0700)應註冊「京北」、拼多多註冊「京南」等等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e7%b6%93%e6%bf%9f/article/20200814/s00002/1597387443976\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e7%25b6%2593%25e6%25bf%259f%2Farticle%2F20200814%2Fs00002%2F1597387443976&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBR9MQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=e2fba66e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e7%25b6%2593%25e6%25bf%259f%2Farticle%2F20200814%2Fs00002%2F1597387443976&h=557eb0f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e7%b6%93%e6%bf%9f/article/20200814/s00002/1597387443976</a>"},{"pid":"23193adc25a0ec943505971bef3646a16fd72966","tid":2155990,"uid":54012,"like":578,"dislike":0,"score":578,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:01:30.000Z","msg":"驚閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1aee07d347dc42184ed6a4b69839c21edf5447","tid":2155990,"uid":364651,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:01:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"014604322fff7541c72e8835a6f3072cd962789d","tid":2155990,"uid":86199,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"23193adc25a0ec943505971bef3646a16fd72966","tid":2155990,"uid":54012,"like":578,"dislike":0,"score":578,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:01:30.000Z","msg":"驚閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"ci